# Nix Configuration

Personal Nix configuration for MacOS.

## Structure
- `flake.nix`: Entry point
- `modules/`: Configuration modules
  - `shell/`: Shell configurations (zsh, terminal)
  - `dev/`: Development tools
  - `apps/`: Applications
  - `system/`: System preferences

## Setup
1. Install Nix
2. Enable flakes
3. Run `nix build .#darwinConfigurations.{hostname}.system`
4. Run `./result/sw/bin/darwin-rebuild switch --flake .`